        </mxCell>
        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0451a5&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;Additional functionalities&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0451a5&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59);&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0451a5&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 data-line=&quot;592&quot; class=&quot;code-line&quot; dir=&quot;auto&quot; id=&quot;webhooks--foodco-calls-mapco&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18); position: relative; color: rgb(32, 32, 32); font-family: -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe WPC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, system-ui, Ubuntu, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Webhooks — Food.co Calls Map.co&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana; font-size: 14px; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;When multiple partners serve the same restaurant, Map.co queries all partners in parallel, deduplicates by restaurant, and picks the best option (fastest delivery, lowest minimum) per restaurant. The user sees one listing, not one per partner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" link="&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#0451a5&quot; data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(4, 81, 165), rgb(118, 185, 255));&quot;&gt;Additional functionalities&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(4, 81, 165)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(4, 81, 165), rgb(118, 185, 255));&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;  Order cancellation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Verdana&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18));&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;6.  Multi-partner deduplication: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;When multiple partners serve the same restaurant, Map.co queries all partners in parallel, deduplicates by restaurant, and picks the best option (fastest delivery, lowest minimum) per restaurant. The user sees one listing, not one per partner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-size: 14px; background-color: light-dark(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(18, 18, 18)); color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186));&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" id="Y1QtjGRFmrKap-deU9kp-179">
