Ubuntu, &amp;quot;Droid Sans&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;On subsequent requests, Map.co sends&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;background-color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); font-size: 1em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; background-color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.12)); padding: 1px 3px; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.357em;&quot;&gt;If-None-Match: &quot;menu_v42&quot;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. If the menu hasn&#39;t changed, the partner returns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-mx-given-colors=&quot;{&amp;quot;color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgb(59, 59, 59)&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;background-color&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)&amp;quot;}&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); font-size: 1em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; background-color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.12)); padding: 1px 3px; border-radius: 4px; line-height: 1.357em;&quot;&gt;304 Not Modified&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: light-dark(rgb(59, 59, 59), rgb(186, 186, 186)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;with no body. If it has changed, the partner returns the full menu with a new ETag.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;" id="Y1QtjGRFmrKap-deU9kp-157">
